title: WSGI Module not working
body:
### System information
- **MacOS  Mojave 10.14**:
- **Python Version 3.6**: 

### Problem
When I execute the manage.py I get the following error related to the WSGI app. I checked the app/settings.py & wsgi.py file and they seem fine.
